videos.description: Penn State's Shep Garner sinks the Nittany Lions' seventh 3-pointer of the game as well as tying the all-time record for made 3-pointers in school history.
videos.headline: Garner ties career 3-point record at Penn State

videos.description: Shep Garner adds to the Nittany Lions' lead after splashing a transition 3-pointer to become the all-time leader in made 3-pointers at Penn State.
videos.headline: Garner sets Penn State's 3-point record

videos.description: Penn State head football coach James Franklin joins broadcast at the NIT semifinals and explains his thoughts on why Saquon Barkley should be the number one overall pick in the upcoming NFL draft.
videos.headline: Franklin says Barkley should be No. 1 pick

videos.description: Penn State's Lamar Stevens drives and tomahawks a dunk plus the foul.
videos.headline: Stevens hammers an and-1 jam

videos.description: Josh Reaves gets the Penn State bench on their feet after Shep Garner tosses up a lob for him to dunk.
videos.headline: Reaves excites bench after alley-oop

videos.description: Penn State head coach Pat Chambers and senior guard Shep Garner break down the Nittany Lions' win over Mississippi State to earn a trip to the NIT championship game.
videos.headline: Chambers: Garner 'is a trail blazer' for Penn State basketball
